name: Original picture of NFT = Nonsense-Fungible Token
description:
1080 × 810 January 14, 2020
 
Progress record to NFT OBJKT/202334 mint.

January 14, 2020. I had a ramen at a ramen shop called 'Keyaki' in New Chitose Airport.
I was so impressed by the taste that after the meal I made a quick sketch on a piece of paper that was in the restaurant.
